*** Settings ***
Resource        imports.resource

Suite Setup     Prepare Suite

Force Tags      no-iframe

*** Variables ***
@{permissions} =    geolocation
...                 midi
...                 notifications
...                 camera
...                 microphone
...                 background-sync
...                 accelerometer
...                 gyroscope
...                 magnetometer
...                 clipboard-read
...                 clipboard-write
